-- Sustainability Indicator: 46,380 Prius Sales
-- B y   T o m   R a n d a l l
-- 2012-10-09T17:38:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-09/sustainability-indicator-74-global-warming-realists.html
Today's sustainability indicator,  46,380 , is the number of Toyota Prius sales in 2012 so far in California, where the fuel-sipping hybrid surpassed the Honda Civic to become the top-selling car. Gas prices in the Golden State are about  76 cents  higher than the national average.  Recent indicators: Visit  www.bloomberg.com/sustainability  for the latest from Bloomberg News about energy, natural resources and global business.